get_socv_rc_variation_factor(25.10)        get_socv_rc_variation_factor(25.10)

Name
       get_socv_rc_variation_factor - Displays the variation factor for inter-
       connect delays

Syntax
       get_socv_rc_variation_factor

       [-help]

       -view <viewName>

       {-early | -late }

       Displays the variation factor for interconnect delays.

Parameters
       -help  Prints out the command usage.

       -early Displays the variation factor for early interconnect delays.

       -late  Displays the variation factor for late interconnect delays.

       -view <viewName>
              Displays  the  SOCV  interconnect variation factor for specified
              view.

Related Information
              * set_socv_rc_variation_factor

